ALGORITHM:-
1) Read the operator
2) Read the operands
3) Using the operator as choice for switch case write case for operators
4) End switch case
5) Stop

Program:
echo "1.Addition 2.Subtraction 3.Multiplication 4.Division"

echo "Enter the operends: "
read a
read b
echo "Enter operator: "
read n
case $n in
"+") echo "$a+$b" = `expr $a + $b`;;
"-") echo "$a-$b" = `expr $a - $b`;;
"*") echo "$a*$b" = `expr $a \* $b`;;
"/") echo "$a/$b" = `expr $a / $b`;;
*) echo "Invalid"

esac
